the insurance management system is the project built using the:
  for frontend - html,css, js
for backend - php and mysql for database connectivity.


the project is all about the insurance polycies and user

the project contains 3 modules:
        1. user 
        2. company
        3. Admin

1. user module:
        in the user module the user is allowed to register and login.
        choosing company of which he wants to buy the insurance of.
        then he see through the company's insurance the return. its rating and other things.
        user can buy, apply for the policy. check the status of that 

2. Company Module:
        this modules allows company to register themselves to the platform.
        add the policy, edit policy, update or can delete the policy
